content.p:
Takes note of the reports of the Secretary-General
A/77/313. and the United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees;
Official Records of the General Assembly, Seventy-seventh Session, Supplement No. 12 (A/77/12).

Recalls the Global Compact on Refugees as set out in the High Commissioner’s annual report (part II) of 2018,
See A/73/12 (Part II). affirmed on 17 December 2018,
See resolution 73/151. and calls upon the international community as a whole, including States and other relevant stakeholders, to implement the Compact in order to achieve its four objectives on an equal footing based on the principle of burden- and responsibility-sharing, and in accordance with the guiding principles and paragraph 4 of the Global Compact on Refugees, through concrete actions, pledges and contributions, including at the first Global Refugee Forum in December 2019, and requests the High Commissioner to report regularly on the progress being made;
